1181
00:58:36,049 --> 00:58:38,920
So it's a טומאה וטהרה Tumah Ve-Tahara for Tumah and Tahara purposes.

1182
00:58:38,920 --> 00:58:42,000
Okay. So the Gemara says והתניא, Ve-Hatanya, one minute, did we not

1183
00:58:42,000 --> 00:58:43,632
