not טמא, Tamei, and that means that it's not considered part of

1187
00:58:50,600 --> 00:58:52,414
him or the mother? So the answer is אי תניא תניא. Ei

1188
00:58:52,414 --> 00:58:53,780
Tanya Tanya. All right. If you got a Baraita, you got a

1189
00:58:53,780 --> 00:58:57,420
Baraita. Then I can't argue. Then you have the evidence. So it

